   "body" : "<h1>Ideas for improving bitcoin mining:</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>it would be interesting if bitcoin mining system could take advantage of:</h2>\r\n- <i>deep learning frameworks, and specially deep convolutional neural networks</i>\r\n\r\n<h2>another interesting thing, specially for lowering the down the mining difficulty ratio would be:</h2>\r\n- <i>allowing users to have their own mining pool, so instead of having community pools, creating a system where mining is only possible, if you do it on a single machine, and it's only possible to use like gpgpu (not heterogeneus computing)</i>\r\n\r\n<h3>that is a good idea becuase:</h3>\r\n- <i>it would make bitcoin mining even more de-centralized</i>",
